Class VOTableFormat.LimitedStarTable

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.starlink.table.AbstractStarTable
      • tap.formatter.VOTableFormat.LimitedStarTable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    uk.ac.starlink.table.StarTable
    Enclosing class:
    VOTableFormat

    public static class VOTableFormat.LimitedStarTable
extends uk.ac.starlink.table.AbstractStarTable

    Special StarTable able to read a fixed maximum number of rows TableIterator. However, if no limit is provided, all rows are read.
